WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:10.875
Well, good morning family. Praise the Lord. It has been an amazing 24 hours. I am just burning with the fire of the Lord today.

00:00:10.876 --> 00:00:19.647
I am so excited to come on here and talk to you and tell you what the Lord did last night.

00:00:19.648 --> 00:00:27.801
I am in awe at what the Lord—I have so many different directions I could go right now.

00:00:27.802 --> 00:00:41.474
But first, I want to tell you all how exciting it is that I heard all the testimonies about the Coachella assassination attempt.

00:00:41.475 --> 00:00:54.763
The sheriff came on there and said he had fake passports, he had fake driver's license plates, he had guns and everything inside of his car.

00:00:54.764 --> 00:01:02.381
They released him on bail for $5,000, but he didn't do anything because God intervened.

00:01:02.382 --> 00:01:09.786
People were like, "Well, where did you prophesy this?"—the doubters. The Lord had me pray very hard for Coachella.

00:01:09.787 --> 00:01:14.955
I kept praying for this word "Coachella,"and I kept getting this in the spirit realm.

00:01:14.956 --> 00:01:19.978
So, I told my friend about it and he helped me Google it. Then my wife helped me Google this word.

00:01:19.979 --> 00:01:25.960
We're going to pray for these major events and big gatherings of people, for nothing to happen.

00:01:25.961 --> 00:01:49.866
The Lord said, "This is how they're going to run their campaign in 2024."And he said, "You need to tell the people to pray and hear the voice of the Lord concerning every place they go in their day-to-day activity, major events, and going with crowds and concerts."That's why I prayed for Coachella.

00:01:49.867 --> 00:01:55.039
The Lord had me praying for this. We'll pray against it for this year.

00:01:55.040 --> 00:01:59.513
I've been praying over Coachella; there are a lot of events to pray over.

00:01:59.514 --> 00:02:08.725
When I warned you all about the shootings at Coachella that were coming up in a couple of days, that was a warning I got this time last year.

00:02:08.726 --> 00:02:17.037
And the Lord told me, "Pray over this. This is a plot from the enemy."I told you about George Soros and these people over there.

00:02:17.038 --> 00:02:27.784
I saw bad men over in Europe having a meeting with the devil at the same time last year when he warned me to pray over Coachella and said that they were plotting something against it.

00:02:27.785 --> 00:02:35.071
The Lord warned me about that and told me to pray for that. I intercede for a lot of things, y'all. But they said, "Well, you've missed it.

00:02:35.072 --> 00:02:58.394
How many things have you gotten to come to pass that the Lord shows you?"And I say, "Man, I've sat on stuff for five years, sometimes longer, before anything ever starts to be in the news."I'm still praying over the thing in Italy the Lord showed me when I warned you all that a major volcano was going to go off and it was going to wipe out the whole coastal city.

00:02:58.395 --> 00:03:04.929
I saw over 300,000 people—boom—dead that fast because of the volcano going off.

00:03:04.930 --> 00:03:11.073
I'm trying to steer you all to show you where I'm at and where I've been praying.

00:03:11.075 --> 00:03:18.052
So, praying over Coachella, and then the Lord was warning me about big gatherings again.

00:03:18.053 --> 00:03:32.399
I was sent an email and even a text from a friend telling me, "Hey, do you remember praying over Coachella?"I got this and I've been praying over Coachella.

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:44.153
The Lord will show me, like I said, way in advance of events trying to manifest, and I take authority over them so that they don't manifest.

00:03:44.154 --> 00:03:59.262
I saw a mass shooting event happening at Coachella and the Lord said, "I want you to pray over this event so that this does not take place."Well, I thought it was the concert event.

00:03:59.263 --> 00:04:04.157
Maybe it was; I don't know. Like I said, we hear in part and we see in part.

00:04:04.158 --> 00:04:09.016
So when you're looking through the filter of what the Lord is trying to tell you, you just keep praying.

00:04:09.017 --> 00:04:13.935
The Lord told me to start praying over this, that this was a serious thing to pray over.

00:04:13.936 --> 00:04:30.712
Well, my friend sent me a text and he said, "Hey Brandon, did you see that President Trump was going to Coachella to hold a rally there?"I had no idea.

00:04:30.713 --> 00:04:45.734
So, with the things that you get in the spirit of warnings and prayer, you try to put your own mind to it and you get in trouble because you're thinking it's the concert. All I know is that's what we pray.

00:04:45.735 --> 00:05:00.159
Whether it was the presidential thing that's going to happen this weekend with the speech and all that, I don't know, because all I know is the Lord warned me and told me to pray over this stuff.

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:06.076
But did it witness with me that this could be it? Yeah. I thought this is probably it.

00:05:06.077 --> 00:05:22.428
More than likely, we were going to pray over Coachella again, this Trump rally that's coming on Saturday, and if there are any plots or any plans, we call them exposed in Jesus'name—that they would be caught in the name of Jesus.

00:05:22.429 --> 00:05:35.198
We call for supernatural wisdom over the Secret Service, supernatural wisdom over the FBI—the good FBI—CIA, Homeland Security, all of them.

00:05:35.199 --> 00:05:41.679
The Riverside County Sheriff's Department just announced an arrest from former President Donald Trump's rally in Coachella.

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:46.991
If you're asking me right now, I probably did have deputies that prevented the third assassination attempt.

00:05:46.992 --> 00:05:53.519
A man carrying several guns and fake passes was stopped by police at a rally in Coachella Valley over the weekend.

00:05:53.520 --> 00:06:06.445
This is not about boasting about my platform, but about warning you to pray and intercede on behalf of America because God is not done with America.

00:06:06.446 --> 00:06:19.599
God is not finished with what he's about to do in America. There is going to be a great harvest of souls beyond anybody's comprehension that's about to come to this land.

00:06:19.600 --> 00:06:32.535
I was thinking about the old Welsh revival and how they said the glory of God came with fire.

00:06:32.536 --> 00:06:53.389
It happened so strongly that the miners who would work in the mines in Wales in that area had to shut down the mines because the mules and the donkeys that were working only knew how to take commands with cuss words.

00:06:53.390 --> 00:07:04.799
But when the fire of God came on those miners and they got the Holy Ghost on their mouths and were delivered from things, they stopped the profanity.

00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:10.297
So, the donkeys and the mules did not know how to respond anymore.

00:07:10.298 --> 00:07:23.999
They had to shut down the mines because the glory came. It took time to train the donkeys and the mules again.

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:52.959
The glory came there, and they were asking one little girl, "What do you feel about what's happened to the revival here?"And she said, "It's like Jesus; we have Sunday every day."All I can say is, "Lord, do it again."There was an awe with the presence of God throughout the whole city.

00:07:52.960 --> 00:08:02.270
There was an awe on every street corner. And I'm telling you, we had revivals in the 1700s with John Wesley and Finney.

00:08:02.271 --> 00:08:13.474
The glory would come so strongly when they would preach in these revivals that they would tell people to get out of the trees because they would climb them to get a better view.

00:08:13.475 --> 00:08:32.718
But John Wesley would warn them to get out of the trees because when he would speak, the glory of God would fill up the outside—not in an inside building—but the presence of the Lord would weigh so strongly that the power of God would knock people out of the trees, and he didn't want them to get hurt.

00:08:32.719 --> 00:08:40.879
I'm telling you, a glory will come again. I'm telling you, an outpouring of his presence is coming again.

00:08:40.880 --> 00:08:46.639
One last call: the Lord warns me and tells me today when I pray.

00:08:46.640 --> 00:08:58.453
Thank God he spared Trump's life again. It was a call to prayer for 30 days. But the enemy has a plan, ladies and gentlemen.

00:08:58.454 --> 00:09:15.199
I've told you even five or six days after the election—if you didn't believe me before, do you believe me now when I tell you the Lord tells me to come on here and warn you about what's coming?

00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:21.838
Maybe this time when you see the next sign, maybe you will listen.

00:09:21.839 --> 00:09:38.891
I pray you do because I'm trying as a watchman on the wall, yelling with all I have to warn you that Jesus Christ is coming—not for anything else, but to warn you that Jesus is coming.

00:09:38.892 --> 00:09:44.644
Jesus is coming, and there is a great outpouring of His Spirit that's coming.

00:09:44.645 --> 00:09:51.754
There is a great shaking to awaken. People don't want to hear about the other side of the coin, the dark side.

00:09:51.755 --> 00:10:04.479
But there are dark days coming, just as there are light days coming. I try very hard now to speak about both.

00:10:04.480 --> 00:10:36.880
But when I have told you about financial crisis, things that I've seen coming—a dollar shaking, worth fifty cents on the dollar, the seizing of the monies in the bank, warning you of a Great Depression with people lined up for miles trying to get food—warning you that I've seen an asteroid hit in the Atlantic Ocean, a great explosion in Poland, and an acceleration of war.

00:10:36.881 --> 00:10:52.754
I've seen Israel attack Iran and the oil, so much so that Saudi Arabia and the BRICS nations will come together stronger against the petrodollar.

00:10:52.755 --> 00:11:05.995
I saw the oil go over two hundred dollars a barrel. I saw gasoline going well over eight, nine, or ten dollars a gallon on average.

00:11:05.996 --> 00:11:13.251
Is it supposed to scare you? No. It's to warn you and to prepare you.

00:11:13.252 --> 00:11:35.205
I bring these things up to warn you, to shake you, to say, 'Listen, we can pray.'I didn't come on this channel to tickle your ears or to entertain you, to make you go, 'Well, that was a really good message; it gave me goosebumps,'and then go back to your apathy, your laziness, and your being slothful and asleep.

00:11:35.206 --> 00:11:43.352
I come on here to shake you, to tell you that there's a plan afoot for the devil's work. But God has a plan that's bigger.

00:11:43.353 --> 00:11:57.119
And if we would plug ourselves in and get excited about what God is going to do in these last days, and humble ourselves and pray and turn from our wicked ways, then He said we would hear from heaven and He would heal our land.

00:11:57.120 --> 00:12:08.793
You all think Donald Trump is going to save America. But there is only one person that will save America, and that is Jesus Christ and an awakening unto God.

00:12:08.794 --> 00:12:25.119
America will not be saved without an awakening unto God. America is in the place where we're trying to change the fruit of America without changing the root.

00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:34.780
And a lot of you think we can just change the fruit, but the problem is the root is bad. Donald Trump isn't going to change the fruit.

00:12:34.781 --> 00:12:46.559
The problem is we're not preaching righteousness and holiness in the pulpits anymore. We preach a lukewarm, seeker-friendly message.

00:12:46.560 --> 00:13:23.039
We're feeding the babies porridge and milk, and they don't have meat to grow because we aren't teaching the Word of God to the people—the meat of the Word, the ABCs of faith—teaching them how to live by faith and how to stay strong, how to cast out devils, to do the Great Commission, to lay hands on the sick and see them recover, to raise the dead, to bring sight to the blind, to open ears, and to tell the lame to leap and walk.

00:13:23.040 --> 00:13:32.559
We have that ability on the inside of us. Jesus Christ lives on the inside of every single one of you.

00:13:32.560 --> 00:13:41.874
And I have such an urgency today, an urgency to tell you like Paul Revere yelling on his horse, 'The British are coming!

00:13:41.875 --> 00:14:03.759
The British are coming!'but to tell you in the midnight hour that I'm riding on the horse through town after town via this YouTube channel, telling the whole world that Jesus Christ is coming, and yet you're still asleep.

00:14:03.760 --> 00:14:09.098
I yell from the mountaintops that Jesus is coming. I had a visitation again last night.

00:14:09.099 --> 00:15:05.246
I cannot tell you what He said this time because it was for me, but I can tell you this: He said, 'A lot of the older generals are going to start to go home, and you're going to see a new generation of Davids rise up.'You will see this shortly: a great move of His presence beyond anything you've ever seen before.

00:15:05.247 --> 00:15:15.518
It's not years away anymore; it's not days away. It's now. You're going to start to see the manifestation of things.

00:15:15.519 --> 00:15:22.719
I'm telling you all, it's time to get your hearts right before the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:15:22.720 --> 00:15:33.518
It's time for you to seek Him like you've never sought Him before.

00:15:33.519 --> 00:15:45.260
Jesus is the healer; He's the same yesterday, today, and forever, and you're about to see it.

00:15:45.261 --> 00:15:56.719
I went to a healing service last night, and the power of God knocked me on my rear.

00:15:56.720 --> 00:16:05.679
My wife and children were all touched by the glory. And we got a word from the minister there.

00:16:05.680 --> 00:16:21.599
We prayed for my little girl Megan, and the glory filled the room.

00:16:21.600 --> 00:16:34.617
You know, when you go and you're not expecting much, you're just excited to be a part of things.

00:16:34.618 --> 00:16:37.735
I never anticipate anything like that—a word from anybody.

00:16:37.736 --> 00:16:43.758
I just go and want to watch someone else get blessed. I'm excited just to be there.

00:16:43.759 --> 00:16:49.380
But he asked for people to come up and tell their testimonies about what God had done for them in the past.

00:16:49.381 --> 00:17:02.799
And I went and told them about taking her to that service a couple of years ago when he prayed for her and, within a week or two, my daughter was completely potty trained.

00:17:02.800 --> 00:17:07.808
Supernaturally, even though the doctors said Megan would never be potty trained.

00:17:07.809 --> 00:17:20.488
They told us that she would maintain the level of eighteen months for the rest of her life and to never expect her to be potty trained.

00:17:20.489 --> 00:17:31.279
There were so many negative things that neuropsychologist said.

00:17:31.280 --> 00:17:34.162
That's when I told him all things are possible to him that believes.

00:17:34.163 --> 00:17:43.105
He told my wife, 'You all are in denial. You need to come to reality.

00:17:43.106 --> 00:18:00.782
I've never seen, in thousands and thousands of cases over thirty or forty years, an autistic child ever healed.'And that's when my wife looked at him and said, 'But my daughter will be.

00:18:00.783 --> 00:18:15.384
She'll be the first, and we're going to come back here and give you a testimony.'Well, we stood and stood, and when there is nothing else to do, you stand.

00:18:15.385 --> 00:18:21.495
Whenever you don't see the fruit of what you're believing for in full manifestation, you keep standing.

00:18:21.496 --> 00:18:29.931
You don't give up. Faith calls those things that be not as though they were. So we believe some more; we keep standing.

00:18:29.932 --> 00:18:36.879
You find your Bible verses, you keep reading them, and you keep believing it.

00:18:36.880 --> 00:18:41.439
Then we had the encounter, and Megan started pottying on the stool.

00:18:41.440 --> 00:18:54.879
Within just a day, she woke up, sat down, and went to the bathroom—that was a miracle in itself, and it's been progressive.

00:18:54.880 --> 00:19:03.993
But a miracle is a miracle even if it's progressive, especially when you realize how far she has come.

00:19:03.994 --> 00:19:14.293
Well, last night we took her again, and he asked if anybody had a testimony.

00:19:14.294 --> 00:19:31.829
So I went down to the front to tell him about Megan, just excited about it, saying, 'God, this is a big deal,'because we spent a lot of money on adult diapers, and they're very expensive.

00:19:31.830 --> 00:19:50.399
He laid hands on her, and the power of God went all over her. He gave us a word about our ministry, gave a word over my wife, and really filled us with fire and encouragement.

00:19:50.400 --> 00:20:06.813
I'm expecting a supernatural turnaround. I'm expecting—I told you there will be a day when my daughter comes on here and tells you all the goodness of our God, that Jesus is the healer.

00:20:06.814 --> 00:20:33.199
He is a healer, and He is going to visit America one last time in a mighty outpouring of His Spirit.

00:20:33.200 --> 00:20:40.897
Coachella was just a prayer assignment. That's the way he deals with me all the time.

00:20:40.898 --> 00:20:46.554
Like I said, the more you get to know me, I come on and do these videos over these 30 days.

00:20:46.555 --> 00:20:52.074
People are asking me to continue to do it afterwards. We'll see; I probably will.

00:20:52.075 --> 00:21:01.371
I feel an urgency to do this more and more. I just thought you all would get tired of it and not show up.

00:21:01.372 --> 00:21:13.597
I mean, honestly, I thought, 'Well, if the people show up and they want to pray, we might as well pray.'You know, whenever people don't show up, it's discouraging.

00:21:13.598 --> 00:21:18.858
You go, 'Well, what's the point?'That is what you think in your natural mind.

00:21:18.859 --> 00:21:25.514
If they're not going to show up and pray, then whatever. But God had an assignment.

00:21:25.515 --> 00:21:30.879
I didn't know what the turnout was going to be, and I really didn't care. He told me to do it.

00:21:30.880 --> 00:21:40.864
He said, 'Do it,'and I said, 'Okay, Lord, I'll do it.'And people are showing up and we're making a difference.

00:21:40.865 --> 00:21:48.074
I'm going to pray today for an outpouring, but we have to take communion first.

00:21:48.075 --> 00:22:03.918
Excuse me. Father, we thank you for your body. We thank you for what you did on that cross 2,000 years ago.

00:22:03.919 --> 00:22:18.658
We thank you that you said, 'By your stripes, I am healed,'from the top of our head to the soles of our feet, Lord. We lift up this body before you, God.

00:22:18.659 --> 00:22:31.519
I thank you that you were wounded for our transgressions, you were bruised for our iniquities, the chastisement of our peace was upon you, and with your stripes, we are healed.

00:22:31.520 --> 00:22:42.347
Megan's healed. Reed is healed. I got a call from a lady who broke her ribs, and I lift up her ribs before you in the name of Jesus.

00:22:42.348 --> 00:22:52.226
I thank you, Father, that you're healing her from the top of her head to her feet. All her ribs are healed in Jesus'name.

00:22:52.227 --> 00:22:59.678
We say supernaturally, put them back together with a creative miracle with no more pain.

00:22:59.679 --> 00:23:19.519
And we say, 'Satan, get your hands off of God's property.'This is his child in Jesus'name.

00:23:19.520 --> 00:23:29.439
Father, I thank you, Lord, for the body right now and we lift it up before you and we thank you.

00:23:29.440 --> 00:23:40.879
We thank you, Father, for what you did for us on Calvary. We take this body right now in Jesus'name.

00:23:40.880 --> 00:23:50.319
Now Lord, we lift up the blood and we thank you. We enter in by the blood of the lamb and by the word of our testimony.

00:23:50.320 --> 00:23:55.945
We have authority over the devil. I thank you for the blood, Lord.

00:23:55.946 --> 00:24:07.222
We take this blood right now in the name of Jesus, and it washes us of our sins and we enter into your throne room with great boldness today as we pray.

00:24:07.223 --> 00:24:15.149
We take our dominion and authority over this earth because you've given us dominion and authority.

00:24:15.150 --> 00:24:39.678
We thank you, Father, that we are washed in the blood, the cleansing blood of the lamb.

00:24:39.679 --> 00:24:46.319
Thank you, Father, for the blood. Thank you for your blood, Lord.

00:24:46.320 --> 00:24:56.576
It never loses its power. We lift up the blood, Father, and we thank you.

00:24:56.577 --> 00:25:09.858
We thank you, Father, for the blood that washes us from all our sins.

00:25:09.859 --> 00:25:14.908
Father, you said to make much of the blood, and the blood will make much of you.

00:25:14.909 --> 00:25:31.918
And we take the blood right now in the name of Jesus. Now Lord, we enter in boldly to your throne.

00:25:31.919 --> 00:25:40.568
I saw in the comment section—my son told me—there's a lady that's believing for healing.

00:25:40.569 --> 00:25:49.999
He said, 'Pray for her.'She really needed prayer for her menopause.

00:25:50.000 --> 00:25:59.819
It's very serious; it's been going on ten years. Ten-year menopause—no more.

00:25:59.820 --> 00:26:15.119
The Lord spoke to me about this and I'm believing with you. The menopause symptoms of ten years are gone now in the name of Jesus.

00:26:15.120 --> 00:26:26.008
We speak to the hormones of this woman who has been bound by these menopausal symptoms for ten years.

00:26:26.009 --> 00:26:31.733
We say healing flow over your body right now in the name of Jesus.

00:26:31.734 --> 00:26:40.496
From the top of your head to the soles of your feet, I pronounce you healed by his stripes.

00:26:40.497 --> 00:26:53.870
We say, 'Bonnie, you are healed. Bonnie, you are delivered. Bonnie, in the name of Jesus, no more of this.'It is a curse.

00:26:53.871 --> 00:26:58.705
This is not living in abundance to the full until it overflows.

00:26:58.706 --> 00:27:08.959
So we speak to the hormones, the pituitary gland, and the glands of the mind to line up in the name of Jesus with the word of God.

00:27:08.960 --> 00:27:16.319
We say in the name of Jesus, hormones line up. Ovaries line up.

00:27:16.320 --> 00:27:24.357
The signals to the body, we call healing in the name of Jesus. We call deliverance in the name of Jesus.

00:27:24.358 --> 00:27:30.933
And we thank you, Father, that you're restoring her body from the top of her head to the soles of her feet.

00:27:30.934 --> 00:27:47.439
No more of this menopause stuff. Father, we thank you for the demonstrations and the manifestations of your glory.

00:27:47.440 --> 00:27:51.868
Lord, we plead the blood over every single person that is represented here.

00:27:51.869 --> 00:27:57.278
