00:27:57.279 --> 00:28:10.193
Father, with your healing touch, nothing's too big and nothing's too small. By his stripes, you are healed in the name of Jesus.

00:28:10.194 --> 00:28:16.598
I thank you, Lord, for the healing power that flows on the inside of them in the name of Jesus.

00:28:16.599 --> 00:28:27.024
I call them healed, I call them whole, I call them well in the name of Jesus—every single one of them.

00:28:27.025 --> 00:28:35.353
Father, I pray over their minds, over their emotions, over every area of their life where they're lacking.

00:28:35.354 --> 00:28:42.798
We thank you, Father, for the healing power that flows on the inside of their bodies.

00:28:42.799 --> 00:28:52.398
I thank you, Lord, for healing arthritis of the necks and all the way down their backs.

00:28:52.399 --> 00:28:59.691
I call them healed and whole, discs in their backs to be restored.

00:28:59.692 --> 00:29:09.994
All the discs and any kind of pain in the backs, on their joints, their knees, their legs, and their ankles.

00:29:09.995 --> 00:29:20.079
Father, all the joints of the body, I call them healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus.

00:29:20.080 --> 00:29:41.119
I thank you, Father, that we take authority over these things and we call those things that be not as though they were. Father, Lord, we speak to the bones in the name of Jesus.

00:29:41.120 --> 00:29:51.236
Now God, I thank you for finances for the people, Father, for the sowers, Father, that they will reap if they faint not.

00:29:51.236 --> 00:30:03.968
And we thank you, Lord. We pray miracle-grow soil on their seed. We speak blessing and increase over their household.

