Now, you can't sit there and complain about your finances if you haven't sown a seed.

00:30:07.772 --> 00:30:23.359
Even if it's like the widow's mite, you have to sow seed. Seedtime and harvest come by whatsoever things you sow that we also reap. Farmers sow a crop to reap a crop.

