Create in us a right standing with you; that Father, we are the head and not the tail and above and not beneath, that we are the salt, Father, in these last days.

01:00:44.435 --> 01:00:56.650
That there would be a great harvest of souls, Father. We call forth the blinded eyes to be opened in the name of Jesus. We speak to the eyes.

01:00:56.651 --> 01:01:07.300
Father, I thank you, Lord, according to Ephesians, that the eyes of their understanding would be enlightened, that they would know what is the hope of the calling.

01:01:07.301 --> 01:01:15.919
We speak to the blinders, for you said in your word that Satan has blinded the eyes of the unbeliever.

01:01:15.920 --> 01:01:30.151
And we speak for the blinders to be removed in the name of Jesus off of their eyes—that the blinders of the eyes would be removed now in the name of Jesus—that they would see.

01:01:30.153 --> 01:01:45.952
We call those eyes to pop open in the name of Jesus. Father, I thank you, Lord, that Satan is no longer able to blind the unbeliever's eyes.

01:01:45.953 --> 01:01:55.759
That there is a moment, a pause in the spirit realm so people can make their own decisions.

01:01:55.760 --> 01:02:19.919
For all the unsaved loved ones and all the people that are represented here that are crying out for their lost family members, we speak for the laborers and the harvesters to go and bring them forth in the name of Jesus, that the angels of the Lord would camp around and about them and make war against the demonic spirits that were causing hindrance for them to come in.

01:02:19.920 --> 01:02:26.558
And we thank you, Lord, that their eyes would see and their ears would hear.

01:02:26.559 --> 01:02:30.569
And those of you that are praying for them, do not give up on them.

01:02:30.570 --> 01:02:41.519
They will come in. For there is one last call, one last call of a harvest.

01:02:41.520 --> 01:02:46.465
Father, I thank you, Lord, for it is the goodness of God that draws man to repentance.

01:02:46.466 --> 01:02:54.719
And I call forth in the name of Jesus healings, demonstrations, and manifestations of the glory.

01:02:54.720 --> 01:03:02.413
Father, I thank you, Lord, for supernatural touches like we saw last night; for great healings will take place.

01:03:02.414 --> 01:03:24.479
Great manifestations and healings will take place in the name of Jesus. Father, I thank you.

01:03:24.480 --> 01:03:46.909
