01:04:39.761 --> 01:05:35.598
There are so many good people; we call forth a harvest, Father. We will not shy back, but we will press forward.

01:05:35.599 --> 01:05:45.679
We will not be ashamed of the Lord Jesus Christ, for great fire will stay on them that believe.

01:05:45.680 --> 01:05:57.279
For you will walk in demonstrations in these days ahead, for there will be an outpouring of my spirit and not dread.

01:05:57.280 --> 01:06:34.318
