01:06:53.119 --> 01:07:01.838
For this is the last call; this is the last hour and you will see my Son's return soon.

01:07:01.839 --> 01:07:17.838
For lift up your eyes and lift up your countenance, for the glory is coming on you.

01:07:17.839 --> 01:08:08.560
Stay. Glory, glory, glory. Do not shy back with the lack, for there will be no lack.

01:08:08.561 --> 01:08:14.764
