01:08:22.861 --> 01:08:33.891
For there is lack."I say, in a moment there will be a transfer—a transfer of my wealth laid up for the righteous.

01:08:33.892 --> 01:08:38.563
Have your ears open to me and you will hear what I've called you to do.

01:08:38.564 --> 01:08:49.005
