01:10:03.120 --> 01:10:13.198
Now is the time to walk in the manifestations and the demonstrations of the glory.

01:10:13.199 --> 01:10:24.639
Rejoice, for many have gone on home before that waited to want to soar like you will soar.

01:10:24.640 --> 01:10:35.439
