01:10:35.440 --> 01:11:05.678
And yet you chose us for such a time as this. I have called you and I have chosen you for such a time as this.

01:11:05.679 --> 01:11:20.959
So don't lose hope. Don't grow weary in well-doing for the best is yet to come.

01:11:20.960 --> 01:13:28.637
Days of heaven on earth you will see. For the glory will rise in thee in a greater way. Lord, we thank you for the manifestation of this.

01:13:28.638 --> 01:13:56.639
We worship you for your demonstrations and manifestations of the glory, arising up as the army, rising up with courage to be filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit.

01:13:56.640 --> 01:14:38.399
Thank you, Father. Glory to your name. See the glory come down.

01:14:38.400 --> 01:15:16.959
