01:15:16.960 --> 01:16:44.079
Oh, Lord, you're beautiful. Your face is all I see. And when your eyes are on this child, your grace abounds to me.

01:16:44.080 --> 01:16:49.379
Oh, Lord, you're beautiful. Your face is all I seek. And when your eyes are on this child, your grace abounds to me.

01:16:49.380 --> 01:24:27.808
Oh, Lord, please light the fire that once burned bright and clear. Father, I thank you.

01:24:27.809 --> 01:24:53.919
It will be birthed out of the spirit before you see it in the natural.

01:24:53.920 --> 01:25:10.238
For the great doors will open. The ancient doors will be opened.

01:25:10.239 --> 01:25:45.996
