01:29:51.040 --> 01:30:59.166
Thank you, Father. Thank you, Lord, for a fresh touch of your glory.

01:30:59.167 --> 01:31:16.054
Father, I thank you that every single person who is believing to be baptized in the Holy Spirit, speaking with other tongues, would have a fresh fire and an outpouring of your spirit on them.

01:31:16.055 --> 01:31:51.491
